## 4. Rollback Plan

### 4.1 CI/CD Rollback

| Scenario | Action |
|----------|--------|
| CI workflow broken | Revert `.github/workflows/ci.yml` to previous commit |
| Deployment broken | Use Vercel dashboard → Deployments → Redeploy previous |
| Branch broken | `git revert` or `git reset` to last known good commit |

### 4.2 Database Rollback

| Scenario | Action |
|----------|--------|
| Bad migration | Run `pnpm db:migrate` with `--rollback` or restore from Neon point-in-time |
| Data corruption | Restore from Neon branch (branches are instant clones) |

### 4.3 Storage Rollback

| Scenario | Action |
|----------|--------|
| Misconfigured bucket | Re-apply settings from this document |
| CloudFront issue | Invalidate cache: `aws cloudfront create-invalidation --distribution-id XXXX --paths "/*"` |

