## 6. Security Considerations

### 6.1 Secrets Management

| Secret | Storage Location | Never In |
|--------|------------------|----------|
| Database credentials | Vercel env vars | Code, .env files in repo |
| AWS credentials | Vercel env vars | Code, .env files in repo |
| CloudFront URLs | Vercel env vars | Can be public (not secret) |

### 6.2 Access Control

| Resource | Access Level |
|----------|--------------|
| S3 buckets | CloudFront only (OAC) |
| Neon database | SSL required, IP allowlist (optional) |
| Vercel | GitHub SSO |

### 6.3 Forbidden Actions

- ❌ Committing secrets to repository
- ❌ Direct S3 public access
- ❌ Unencrypted database connections
- ❌ Sharing IAM credentials

