## 8. Troubleshooting

### 8.1 Common Issues

| Issue | Cause | Solution |
|-------|-------|----------|
| CI fails on lint | ESLint errors | Fix errors locally, push again |
| CI fails on types | TypeScript errors | Fix errors locally, push again |
| CI fails on build | Missing env vars | Add dummy `DATABASE_URL` in workflow |
| Vercel deploy fails | Missing env vars | Set all required vars in Vercel dashboard |
| S3 403 error | Bucket policy wrong | Re-apply policy from Section 3.4 |
| CloudFront 403 | OAC not configured | Check distribution origin settings |
| Database connection fails | Wrong connection string | Verify pooled vs unpooled usage |

